          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": "★★★★★",
            "text": "\"I've been treating acne for years and tried so many products. AntiAcne is one that actually works! I noticed changes after just one week. After a month, my skin is brighter, more even, and my pores are reduced.\"",
            "author": "Eliška F.",
